ChangeLog for Simple Chat Client
========================= 

Version 1.5.0 (unknown)
================================
* Changed channel settings layout
* Added tray notification
* Added punish reason
* Added channel avatars
* Added debug window
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.4.0 (10.03.2012)
================================
* Added avatars support
* Added minimize to tray
* Movable tabs
* Added highlight
* Added copy link to clipboard
* Enabled DEP (permanent) and ASLR on windows
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.1.3 (05.12.2011)
================================
* Fixed priv logs
* Added themes
* Added youtube player
* Added reverse colors
* Added find text
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.1.2 (10.09.2011)
================================
* Animated emoticons work again
* Removed embedded styles
* Removed find text dialog
* Fixed cycle command
* Fixed bug in connect
* Fixed reconnecting
* Removed detect already running
* Fixed detect kamerzysta
* Fixed linux webcam refresh
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.1.1 (21.07.2011)
================================
* Added profiles
* New crypt
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.1.0 (09.07.2011)
================================
* Added /mp3 command
* Fixed update
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.0.13 (30.06.2011)
================================
* Fixed offline messages
* Added button Find text
* Added button Send to notes
* Added shortcut ctrl+tab and ctrl+shift+tab
* Changed main layout
* Fixed cam support in linux
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.0.12 (20.05.2011)
================================
* Added auto-away
* New nicklist
* Fixed logs - default saved by date
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.0.11 (29.04.2011)
================================

* Fixed auth
* Added menu "open link"
* Added offline messages support
* Many bugfixes

Version 1.0.10 (14.04.2011)
================================

* Fixed pasting multi-line
* Fixed lag
* Fixed classic style
* Fixed network reconnect
* Added my profile
* Fixed config
* Added linux reading cam frame using v4l2
* Added age check for Erotic channels
* Fixed options layout
* Fixed kamerzysta support
* Added user stats 
* Added channel stats 
* Fixed network quit
* Added basic syntax highlighter
* Added detect already running scc
* Added background image
* Added awaylog
* Added basic cam support for linux
* Many bugfixes
